### Pattern 3: Command Workflow Chaining
/agentos → /agentos-start → /agentos-plan → /agentos-execute → /agentos-verify → /agentos-complete

### Pattern 4: Two-Layer Validation
Semantic understanding → MCP structure validation → Subagent coherence validation

